        "description": {
          "chatFlavor": "<div class=\"garou-rite\">   <h3>Rite of Cleansing</h3>   <p><em>Rite of Accord (Level 1)</em></p>    <hr>    <p><strong>Time:</strong> 30 minutes<br>   <strong>Cost:</strong> 3 Gnosis (spent on attempt)<br>   <strong>Focus:</strong> Pure water, ash, smoke, or soil from an untainted place<br>   <strong>Target:</strong> One willing creature you touch</p>    <p><strong>Roll:</strong> Gnosis Roll (d20 + Max Gnosis rating)<br>   <strong>DC:</strong> 13 (minor impurity) or 15 (severe impurity)</p>    <hr>    <p><strong>On Success — choose ONE:</strong></p>   <ul>     <li>Remove <strong>Poisoned</strong> (only if disease/toxin/supernatural corruption)</li>     <li>Remove <strong>Frightened</strong> (only if supernatural/spiritual source)</li>     <li>Remove <strong>Charmed</strong> (only if supernatural/spiritual source)</li>     <li>Reduce <strong>Exhaustion</strong> by 1 (only spiritual strain/corruption/supernatural influence)</li>     <li>Cleanse one lingering <strong>minor curse</strong> or corrupting effect (ST adjudication)</li>   </ul>    <p><strong>Limitations:</strong></p>   <ul>     <li>Cannot cure mundane disease</li>     <li>Cannot remove paralysis, petrification, blindness, or deafness</li>     <li>Cannot remove major curses (remove curse+ required)</li>     <li>A creature can benefit from this Rite only once per long rest</li>   </ul>    <p><strong>On Failure:</strong> Gnosis is spent. The condition remains. No worsening.</p>    <hr>    <p style=\"opacity:0.7; font-size:0.85em;\">     [GAROU_RITE_USE] id=cleansing; category=accord; tier=1; dc=13|15   </p> </div>"
