    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"625\" data-end=\"646\">Rite of Cleansing</strong><br data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"649\" /><em data-start=\"649\" data-end=\"675\">Rite of Accord • Level 1</em></p><p data-start=\"677\" data-end=\"946\"><strong data-start=\"677\" data-end=\"704\">Minimum Maximum Gnosis:</strong> 4<br data-start=\"706\" data-end=\"709\" /><strong data-start=\"709\" data-end=\"725\">Gnosis Cost:</strong> 3<br data-start=\"727\" data-end=\"730\" /><strong data-start=\"730\" data-end=\"739\">Time:</strong> 30 minutes<br data-start=\"750\" data-end=\"753\" /><strong data-start=\"753\" data-end=\"768\">Resolution:</strong> Wisdom Check (Gnosis Roll)<br data-start=\"795\" data-end=\"798\" /><strong data-start=\"798\" data-end=\"805\">DC:</strong> 13 (minor impurity), 15 (severe impurity)<br data-start=\"847\" data-end=\"850\" /><strong data-start=\"850\" data-end=\"867\">Participants:</strong> One Garou<br data-start=\"877\" data-end=\"880\" /><strong data-start=\"880\" data-end=\"890\">Focus:</strong> Pure water, ash, smoke, or soil from an untainted place</p><hr data-start=\"948\" data-end=\"951\" /><h3 data-start=\"953\" data-end=\"963\">Effect</h3><p data-start=\"964\" data-end=\"1115\">You perform a ceremonial purification to remove temporary spiritual or physical afflictions caused by imbalance, corruption, or supernatural influence.</p><p data-start=\"1117\" data-end=\"1225\">On a successful check, you may remove <strong data-start=\"1155\" data-end=\"1162\">one</strong> of the following conditions from a willing creature you touch:</p><ul data-start=\"1227\" data-end=\"1539\"><li data-start=\"1227\" data-end=\"1304\"><p data-start=\"1229\" data-end=\"1304\">Poisoned <em data-start=\"1238\" data-end=\"1302\">(only if caused by disease, toxin, or supernatural corruption)</em></p></li><li data-start=\"1305\" data-end=\"1371\"><p data-start=\"1307\" data-end=\"1371\">Frightened <em data-start=\"1318\" data-end=\"1369\">(only if the source is supernatural or spiritual)</em></p></li><li data-start=\"1372\" data-end=\"1435\"><p data-start=\"1374\" data-end=\"1435\">Charmed <em data-start=\"1382\" data-end=\"1433\">(only if the source is supernatural or spiritual)</em></p></li><li data-start=\"1436\" data-end=\"1539\"><p data-start=\"1438\" data-end=\"1539\">1 level of exhaustion <em data-start=\"1460\" data-end=\"1537\">(only if caused by spiritual strain, corruption, or supernatural influence)</em></p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1541\" data-end=\"1675\">Alternatively, instead of removing a condition, you may cleanse a creature of one lingering <strong data-start=\"1633\" data-end=\"1648\">minor curse</strong> or corrupting effect that:</p><ul data-start=\"1676\" data-end=\"1845\"><li data-start=\"1676\" data-end=\"1715\"><p data-start=\"1678\" data-end=\"1715\">does not impose permanent penalties</p></li><li data-start=\"1716\" data-end=\"1769\"><p data-start=\"1718\" data-end=\"1769\">does not require <em data-start=\"1735\" data-end=\"1749\">remove curse</em> or stronger magic</p></li><li data-start=\"1770\" data-end=\"1845\"><p data-start=\"1772\" data-end=\"1845\">is thematically tied to Wyrm-tainted, necromantic, or abyssal influence</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1847\" data-end=\"1902\">The Storyteller determines whether an effect qualifies.</p><hr data-start=\"1904\" data-end=\"1907\" /><h3 data-start=\"1909\" data-end=\"1924\">Limitations</h3><p data-start=\"1925\" data-end=\"1942\">This Rite cannot:</p><ul data-start=\"1943\" data-end=\"2133\"><li data-start=\"1943\" data-end=\"1980\"><p data-start=\"1945\" data-end=\"1980\">remove diseases of mundane origin</p></li><li data-start=\"1981\" data-end=\"2040\"><p data-start=\"1983\" data-end=\"2040\">remove petrification, paralysis, blindness, or deafness</p></li><li data-start=\"2041\" data-end=\"2102\"><p data-start=\"2043\" data-end=\"2102\">remove curses that require <em data-start=\"2070\" data-end=\"2084\">remove curse</em> or higher magic</p></li><li data-start=\"2103\" data-end=\"2133\"><p data-start=\"2105\" data-end=\"2133\">affect unwilling creatures</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"2135\" data-end=\"2201\">A creature can benefit from this Rite only <strong data-start=\"2178\" data-end=\"2200\">once per long rest</strong>.</p><hr data-start=\"2203\" data-end=\"2206\" /><h3 data-start=\"2208\" data-end=\"2219\">Failure</h3><p data-start=\"2220\" data-end=\"2238\">On a failed check:</p><ul data-start=\"2239\" data-end=\"2350\"><li data-start=\"2239\" data-end=\"2262\"><p data-start=\"2241\" data-end=\"2262\">The Gnosis is spent</p></li><li data-start=\"2263\" data-end=\"2288\"><p data-start=\"2265\" data-end=\"2288\">The condition remains</p></li><li data-start=\"2289\" data-end=\"2350\"><p data-start=\"2291\" data-end=\"2350\">Spirits may show mild displeasure at improper performance</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"2352\" data-end=\"2388\">Failure never worsens the condition.</p><hr data-start=\"2390\" data-end=\"2393\" /><p data-start=\"2395\" data-end=\"2576\"><strong data-start=\"2395\" data-end=\"2419\">Tag (do not remove):</strong><br data-start=\"2419\" data-end=\"2422\" /><code data-start=\"2422\" data-end=\"2576\">[GAROU_RITE] category=accord; id=cleansing; tier=1; minMaxGnosis=4; cost=3gnosis; time=30m; resolution=wisdom; dc=13|15; target=touch; limit=1/target/lr</code></p>",
      "chat": "<p><strong data-start=\"625\" data-end=\"646\">Rite of Cleansing</strong><br data-start=\"646\" data-end=\"649\" /><em data-start=\"649\" data-end=\"675\">Rite of Accord • Level 1</em></p><p data-start=\"677\" data-end=\"946\"><strong data-start=\"677\" data-end=\"704\">Minimum Maximum Gnosis:</strong> 4<br data-start=\"706\" data-end=\"709\" /><strong data-start=\"709\" data-end=\"725\">Gnosis Cost:</strong> 3<br data-start=\"727\" data-end=\"730\" /><strong data-start=\"730\" data-end=\"739\">Time:</strong> 30 minutes<br data-start=\"750\" data-end=\"753\" /><strong data-start=\"753\" data-end=\"768\">Resolution:</strong> Wisdom Check (Gnosis Roll)<br data-start=\"795\" data-end=\"798\" /><strong data-start=\"798\" data-end=\"805\">DC:</strong> 13 (minor impurity), 15 (severe impurity)<br data-start=\"847\" data-end=\"850\" /><strong data-start=\"850\" data-end=\"867\">Participants:</strong> One Garou<br data-start=\"877\" data-end=\"880\" /><strong data-start=\"880\" data-end=\"890\">Focus:</strong> Pure water, ash, smoke, or soil from an untainted place</p><hr data-start=\"948\" data-end=\"951\" /><h3 data-start=\"953\" data-end=\"963\">Effect</h3><p data-start=\"964\" data-end=\"1115\">You perform a ceremonial purification to remove temporary spiritual or physical afflictions caused by imbalance, corruption, or supernatural influence.</p><p data-start=\"1117\" data-end=\"1225\">On a successful check, you may remove <strong data-start=\"1155\" data-end=\"1162\">one</strong> of the following conditions from a willing creature you touch:</p><ul data-start=\"1227\" data-end=\"1539\"><li data-start=\"1227\" data-end=\"1304\"><p data-start=\"1229\" data-end=\"1304\">Poisoned <em data-start=\"1238\" data-end=\"1302\">(only if caused by disease, toxin, or supernatural corruption)</em></p></li><li data-start=\"1305\" data-end=\"1371\"><p data-start=\"1307\" data-end=\"1371\">Frightened <em data-start=\"1318\" data-end=\"1369\">(only if the source is supernatural or spiritual)</em></p></li><li data-start=\"1372\" data-end=\"1435\"><p data-start=\"1374\" data-end=\"1435\">Charmed <em data-start=\"1382\" data-end=\"1433\">(only if the source is supernatural or spiritual)</em></p></li><li data-start=\"1436\" data-end=\"1539\"><p data-start=\"1438\" data-end=\"1539\">1 level of exhaustion <em data-start=\"1460\" data-end=\"1537\">(only if caused by spiritual strain, corruption, or supernatural influence)</em></p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1541\" data-end=\"1675\">Alternatively, instead of removing a condition, you may cleanse a creature of one lingering <strong data-start=\"1633\" data-end=\"1648\">minor curse</strong> or corrupting effect that:</p><ul data-start=\"1676\" data-end=\"1845\"><li data-start=\"1676\" data-end=\"1715\"><p data-start=\"1678\" data-end=\"1715\">does not impose permanent penalties</p></li><li data-start=\"1716\" data-end=\"1769\"><p data-start=\"1718\" data-end=\"1769\">does not require <em data-start=\"1735\" data-end=\"1749\">remove curse</em> or stronger magic</p></li><li data-start=\"1770\" data-end=\"1845\"><p data-start=\"1772\" data-end=\"1845\">is thematically tied to Wyrm-tainted, necromantic, or abyssal influence</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1847\" data-end=\"1902\">The Storyteller determines whether an effect qualifies.</p><hr data-start=\"1904\" data-end=\"1907\" /><h3 data-start=\"1909\" data-end=\"1924\">Limitations</h3><p data-start=\"1925\" data-end=\"1942\">This Rite cannot:</p><ul data-start=\"1943\" data-end=\"2133\"><li data-start=\"1943\" data-end=\"1980\"><p data-start=\"1945\" data-end=\"1980\">remove diseases of mundane origin</p></li><li data-start=\"1981\" data-end=\"2040\"><p data-start=\"1983\" data-end=\"2040\">remove petrification, paralysis, blindness, or deafness</p></li><li data-start=\"2041\" data-end=\"2102\"><p data-start=\"2043\" data-end=\"2102\">remove curses that require <em data-start=\"2070\" data-end=\"2084\">remove curse</em> or higher magic</p></li><li data-start=\"2103\" data-end=\"2133\"><p data-start=\"2105\" data-end=\"2133\">affect unwilling creatures</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"2135\" data-end=\"2201\">A creature can benefit from this Rite only <strong data-start=\"2178\" data-end=\"2200\">once per long rest</strong>.</p><hr data-start=\"2203\" data-end=\"2206\" /><h3 data-start=\"2208\" data-end=\"2219\">Failure</h3><p data-start=\"2220\" data-end=\"2238\">On a failed check:</p><ul data-start=\"2239\" data-end=\"2350\"><li data-start=\"2239\" data-end=\"2262\"><p data-start=\"2241\" data-end=\"2262\">The Gnosis is spent</p></li><li data-start=\"2263\" data-end=\"2288\"><p data-start=\"2265\" data-end=\"2288\">The condition remains</p></li><li data-start=\"2289\" data-end=\"2350\"><p data-start=\"2291\" data-end=\"2350\">Spirits may show mild displeasure at improper performance</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"2352\" data-end=\"2388\">Failure never worsens the condition.</p><hr data-start=\"2390\" data-end=\"2393\" /><p data-start=\"2395\" data-end=\"2576\"><strong data-start=\"2395\" data-end=\"2419\">Tag (do not remove):</strong><br data-start=\"2419\" data-end=\"2422\" /><code data-start=\"2422\" data-end=\"2576\">[GAROU_RITE] category=accord; id=cleansing; tier=1; minMaxGnosis=4; cost=3gnosis; time=30m; resolution=wisdom; dc=13|15; target=touch; limit=1/target/lr</code></p>"
